These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, blend
House: futuristic, cottage
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, metal
2 different pets are kept: goat, hamster
1. the fonseca-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the fan of soul is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
3. the futuristic house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Cigar       | blend       | fonseca |
| House         | cottage | futuristic  |
| Music-Genre       | metal    | soul    |
| Pet   | hamster       | goat      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There 2 different types of food: raspberry, asparagus
2 different pets are kept: hamster, lizard
2 different games are played: poker, domino
There are 2 different favourite colors: amber, lilac
1. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1
3. the person playing poker is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Food      | asparagus     | raspberry |
| Pet           | hamster | lizard      |
| Game   | domino  | poker      |
| Color         | amber | lilac     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: blue, ivory
The people have 2 different jobs:  engineer, dressmaker
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: satire, drama
2 different games are played: billiard, go
1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
2. the person who likes blue is the person playing go##1
3. the engineer is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Color      | blue | ivory  |
| Job          | engineer    | dressmaker   |
| Movie-Genre   | drama  | satire   |
| Game     | go     | billiard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: february, december
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, bongani
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, train
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, azalea
1. the person who growsdahlia is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is the chaman-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Birthday      | february       | december |
| Cigar          | bongani         | chaman    |
| Transport           | train | tram    |
| Flower   | dahlia           | azalea   |

 #################################

 
