.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
There 2 different types of food: artichoke, watermelon
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, poppy
City: new-york, hamburg
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, havana
1. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the havana-smoker##1
3. the person traveling to new-york is the person eating watermelon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Food           | watermelon | artichoke     |
| Flower   | daisy          | poppy |
| City           | new-york          | hamburg    |
| Cigar     | havana            | old-henry       |

 